caption.p: Relative expression levels of the ADCY1 protein in SH-SY5Y cells treated with 1,8-cineole ( A) and Laurus nobilis essential oil ( B). Each panel shows the densitometry of bands in the treated groups and control. Values are the mean ± SD in each group ( n = 3). * p < 0.05, compared to control (ANOVA followed by Dunnett’s multiple comparison test).
